	<p class="description">Hi there! I'm Deepak Bora, a passionate and dedicated artist specializing in "portrait painting", "digital illustration", “custom artworks”,etc. Art has been my lifelong love since 8yrs, and I am thrilled to share my artworks with you.</p>
</div>

<div class="wrapper">
	<h2 class="sub-heading">My Artistic Journey</h2>
	<p class="description">Like most of the people I was also bad at art but due to one of my classmate who made a lot of fun of my art for a whole day. I started improving it and after sometime even the whole class got to know that I am out of their league Today he’s one of them who asks about my latest artwork photographs to show their friends. Over the years, I have honed my skills and still developing my unique style that blends "traditional techniques with modern elements".</p>
</div>

<div class="wrapper">
	<h2 class="sub-heading">What I Offer</h2>
	<p class="description">I specialize in creating custom artwork that resonates with your personal story or vision. Whether it's a portrait to celebrate a loved one, a landscape to bring peace to your home, or an abstract piece to add a splash of color to your space, I am here to bring your ideas to life.</p>
</div>

<div class="wrapper">
	<h2 class="sub-heading">My Process</h2>
	<p class="description">Each commission is a collaborative journey. I start by understanding your vision through detailed conversations and reference materials. Once we have a clear concept, I provide preliminary sketches for your approval. Throughout the creation process, I keep you updated with progress shots to ensure the final piece exceeds your expectations.</p>
